{
  "video_id": "6gi3EEeR92g",
  "title": "5 Ways to Get \"Post-Conviction Relief\" for Immigration Purposes",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6210.0,
      "end_time": 8770.0,
      "text": "Any time someone who&#39;s not a citizen of the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8770.0,
      "end_time": 12620.0,
      "text": "is convicted of a crime, and later-- sometimes years later--"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 12620.0,
      "end_time": 16291.0,
      "text": "they find that it has triggered immigration consequences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16292.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18250.0,
      "text": "that is they&#39;re about to be deported or removed"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18250.0,
      "end_time": 19940.0,
      "text": "from the United States, they&#39;re not"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19940.0,
      "end_time": 21930.0,
      "text": "allowed renter the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 21930.0,
      "end_time": 24250.0,
      "text": "they can&#39;t adjust their status, or they&#39;re not"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24250.0,
      "end_time": 27730.0,
      "text": "allowed to naturalize and become a citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27730.0,
      "end_time": 29930.0,
      "text": "But in many of these situations, there"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 29930.0,
      "end_time": 33400.0,
      "text": "are avenues of what we call post-conviction relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33400.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "That is ways that we can go back retroactively and attack"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39470.0,
      "text": "or negate the conviction in order"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39470.0,
      "end_time": 42480.0,
      "text": "to avoid those immigration consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42480.0,
      "end_time": 44230.0,
      "text": "And in this video, I&#39;m going to talk"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44230.0,
      "end_time": 48129.0,
      "text": "about the five most common and typical ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48130.0,
      "end_time": 50100.0,
      "text": "to get post conviction relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50100.0,
      "end_time": 53450.0,
      "text": "The first is to run a motion to overturn or vacate"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53450.0,
      "end_time": 56630.0,
      "text": "the conviction based on ineffective assistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 56630.0,
      "end_time": 57410.0,
      "text": "of counsel."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57410.0,
      "end_time": 59870.0,
      "text": "Basically, saying that the defense attorney was"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59870.0,
      "end_time": 61349.0,
      "text": "incompetent."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61350.0,
      "end_time": 64800.0,
      "text": "The second is resentencing for conviction"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64800.0,
      "end_time": 65990.0,
      "text": "for an aggravated felony."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 65990.0,
      "end_time": 67994.0,
      "text": "Now, usually aggravated felonies are"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 67995.0,
      "end_time": 71194.0,
      "text": "only deportable if there&#39;s a sentence of one year or more."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71194.0,
      "end_time": 72610.0,
      "text": "So sometimes we can go in and have"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 72610.0,
      "end_time": 77430.0,
      "text": "the person resentenced to 364 days in jail--"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77430.0,
      "end_time": 78730.0,
      "text": "just under a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78730.0,
      "end_time": 81420.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;ll do the trick and avoid deportation."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81420.0,
      "end_time": 85300.0,
      "text": "The third is to reduce a felony to a misdemeanor."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85300.0,
      "end_time": 88450.0,
      "text": "The fourth is a motion to withdraw a guilty plea"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88450.0,
      "end_time": 90140.0,
      "text": "or no contest plea."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90140.0,
      "end_time": 93110.0,
      "text": "And the fifth is a habeas corpus petition"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93110.0,
      "end_time": 96190.0,
      "text": "in a situation where the person is still in custody."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 96190.0,
      "end_time": 97840.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re in one of these situations"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97840.0,
      "end_time": 100450.0,
      "text": "where you have a conviction that&#39;s causing immigration"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100450.0,
      "end_time": 103910.0,
      "text": "consequences, you want to be sure and get an attorney who"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103910.0,
      "end_time": 107500.0,
      "text": "understands not only criminal law, but immigration law"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107500.0,
      "end_time": 108330.0,
      "text": "as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108330.0,
      "end_time": 110550.0,
      "text": "Because the system is complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110550.0,
      "end_time": 112220.0,
      "text": "but there are a lot of different ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 112220.0,
      "end_time": 115130.0,
      "text": "to attack the prior conviction to obtain"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115130.0,
      "end_time": 116940.0,
      "text": "post conviction relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 116940.0,
      "end_time": 120270.0,
      "text": "And ultimately, to keep you in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 120270.0,
      "end_time": 123800.0,
      "text": "and keep you on a track where you have an opportunity to gain"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123800.0,
      "end_time": 124236.0,
      "text": "citizenship."
    }
  ]
